<br>
If you are using MA special attacks such as BwT, for example, be sure and follow Viirruss' advice and add the nano damage to your total...since the special attack damage will be nano damage and not summed into your total damage (AODD has to track it separately).<br>
<br>
Remember, I am not advocating you ditch claws altogether.  My MA used a claw until about 130th level.  They are a great weapon, and I would often use them in conjunction with BwT by simply dropping the claw onto the hotbar for easy unequipping/equipping during combat.  <br>
<br>
But you should typically only use ONE claw, and then only if certain conditions apply: 1) Your Phys Init is 300+, 2) Your Piercing is kept maxxed at ALL TIMES, 3) You implant for Piercing to keep it as high as possible so it doesn't lag too far behind your MA attack rating, and 4) if you ALWAYS have the highest level claw you can self-equip.<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
